             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am clerk to the prosecutor: I went with the last witness, and I took this bag of shot from the prisoner; the bag was marked No. 3, I believe it to be Mr. Price's property.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I picked it up.</p>
